column16: Melky Cabrera grounds out to first baseman Austin Romine.
Willy Garcia singles on a sharp ground ball to catcher Gary Sanchez, deflected by pitcher Ronald Herrera.
Omar Narvaez grounds out sharply, first baseman Austin Romine to pitcher Ronald Herrera.
Albert Pujols called out on strikes.
Kole Calhoun lines out to center fielder Aaron Hicks.
Cameron Maybin grounds out softly, pitcher Ronald Herrera to first baseman Matt Holliday.   Juan Graterol to 2nd.
Juan Graterol singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Brett Gardner.
Danny Espinosa called out on strikes.
Eric Young Jr.   hit by pitch.
Andrelton Simmons homers (7) on a fly ball to left center field.   Luis Valbuena scores.
Yunel Escobar grounds out, third baseman Chase Headley to first baseman Matt Holliday.
Albert Pujols grounds out sharply, second baseman Starlin Castro to first baseman Matt Holliday.
